-- Hochtief Hires Goldman to Advise on Defense Strategy, Financial Times Says
-- B y   A n g e l a   C u l l e n
-- 2010-09-21T07:01:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-21/hochtief-hires-goldman-to-advise-on-defense-strategy-financial-times-says.html
Hochtief AG hired Goldman Sachs
Group Inc. as a second banking adviser as it seeks to defend
itself against a takeover by Actividades de Construccion &
Servicios SA, Financial Times reported, citing two unidentified
people close to the situation.  Goldman joins Credit Suisse Group AG, which has advised the
German construction company over the past two years, FT said. 